data.title: Bondi Icebergs – Bondi Icebergs Club & Swim School
data.text:
A Rich History

Founded in 1929

As the only licensed Swimming Club in the world, Icebergs has a rich history & some very famous club alumni. Come & visit our premises to find out for yourself who are in the company you could keep!

our food & drink

Enjoy a few with a view

We think its hard to find a better view in Sydney - maybe even the world. Book a table or come on in - walk-ins welcomed!

our memberships

Come & join our club

Social

Up to 10% off all drinks & discounts on food. It pays for itself!

Book a table

Bondi Icebergs Club has a rich history of creating memories that last a lifetime. Are you looking for a location for your next lunch or dinner? Maybe you want to enjoy a cocktail with a view? We think our club has the best view in the world!
